description: Precicion Trim, Inc. operates in the machine automation and development field. The company designs, manufactures, and distributes robotic and non-robotic machines in various industries. It also owns medical devices, and has a contract for a robotic bud trimming device that would revolutionize marijuana trimming. The company was formerly known as Eastern Environment Solutions, Corp. and changed its name to Precicion Trim, Inc. in July 2016. Precicion Trim, Inc. is based in Huntington Beach, California.
